<h1>
OS/2 Information Reference Library
</h1>
</center>
<hr>
This information is provided for your information only and is copyright
by IBM Corporation.  Making this information available on the World Wide
Web might allow persons who are interested in information on OS/2 to
take a look at the manuals and capabilities of OS/2 before purchasing.
</p>

<p>
Please remember that this system is running on OS/2 WARP SERVER and only
has a single ISDN B-Channel connection to the internet, so limited
bandwidth is available.

