<center>
<h1>Keith Medcalf & Associates</h1>
</center>

<p>
Keith Medcalf & Associates is a consulting company operated by Keith
Medcalf dealing primarily with Networking and Applications support.
Keith Medcalf has many years experience in all aspects of the computer
field ranging from application development, analysis and design, to help
desk operations and LAN support; on a variety of platforms running the
range from Solaris to DOS, Windows and Windows NT to OS/2.
</p>
<br>
