<HTML>
<TITLE>DB2 WWW Connection Celdial demonstration </TITLE>
<img src="/icons/head1.gif">   
<body>
 
<H1>Welcome to the Celdial home page</H1>
 
<P>This demonstration shows some basic capabilities of
DB2 World Wide Web Connection using a sample database.
In the demonstration, Celdial allows people to view, update,
and even change information in their database.
<HR>
 
<P>Please choose one of the following: 
<DL>
  <DD>
  <A HREF="curcust.htm"> Order information </A>
<P>
  <DD>
  <A HREF="sales.htm"> Sales Support</A>
<P>
  <DD>
  <A HREF="person.htm"> Marketing Personnel (This is image and long string demo. This is for DB2 V2.1 only)</A>
</DL>
<P>
<hr>
<p>
Other pages of interest:
<P>
<A href="celdemo.htm">DB2 WWW Connection Demonstrations</A>
<br>
<A href="http://www.software.ibm.com/data/db2/db2wfac2.html">DB2 WWW Connection Home Page</A>
<P>
