<TITLE>DB2 WWW Connection Customer Registration Demo</TITLE>
<img src="/icons/head1.gif">   
<body>
<H1>Welcome to the DB2 WWW Connection Customer Registration Demo</H1>
<P>
This demonstration shows how to use DB2 WWW Connection to keep a 
database of customers.  You can
add (insert), update, delete, and query customers in the database.
<HR>
<P>
Please choose one of the following: 
<P>
<UL>
<LI> <A HREF="/cgi-bin/db2www.exe/regquery.d2w/input">Query/Update/Delete Existing Customers</A>
<p>
<LI> <A HREF="/cgi-bin/db2www.exe/regtquer.d2w/input">Query Existing Customers Using HTML 3.0 Tables</A>
<p>
<LI> <A HREF="/cgi-bin/db2www.exe/register.d2w/input">Add a New Customer</A>
</UL>
<hr>
<p>
Other pages of interest:
<P>
<A href="celdemo.htm">DB2 WWW Connection Demonstrations</A>
<br>
<A href="http://www.software.ibm.com/data/db2/db2wfac2.html">DB2 WWW Connection Home Page</A>
<P>
