<H1><A NAME="Header_34" HREF="icswgmst.html#ToC_34">Advanced Configuration</A></H1>
<HR>
<H1><A NAME="HDRCFR" HREF="icswgmst.html#ToC_35">Using the configuration file</A></H1>
<P>
This chapter describes each server
configuration directive.
If you choose to configure the server by
editing the httpd.cnf configuration file, use this
chapter as a reference.
If you choose to configure your server by using the Configuration
and Administration forms, you do not need to refer to this chapter.
<P>
The directive descriptions are grouped according to function,
similar to the way the
Configuration and Administration forms are grouped.
Within each group, the directives are in alphabetical order.
<P>
<P>Partial Table-of-Contents
<MENU>
