<LI><A NAME=ToC_111 HREF="#HDRDIRSWSZ" >DirShowSize - Show file size on directory listings</A>
<LI><A NAME=ToC_114 HREF="#HDRICONPAT" >IconPath - Specify the path for the directory listing internal icons</A>
<LI><A NAME=ToC_117 HREF="#HDRWELCO" >Welcome - Specify names of welcome files</A>
