<MENU>
<LI><A NAME=ToC_314 HREF="#HDRDELESCR" >DELETE-Script - Specify the location and name of accessory script for DELETE requests</A>
<LI><A NAME=ToC_317 HREF="#HDRPOSTSCR" >POST-Script - Specify the location and name of accessory script for POST requests</A>
<LI><A NAME=ToC_320 HREF="#HDRPUTSCR" >PUT-Script - Specify the location and name of accessory script for PUT requests</A>
<LI><A NAME=ToC_323 HREF="#HDRSEARCH" >Search - Specify location of search script</A>
</MENU>
<LI><A NAME=ToC_326 HREF="#HDRMETA" >Meta-Information - Name meta-information files and directories</A>
<MENU>
<LI><A NAME=ToC_327 HREF="#HDRMETADIR" >MetaDir - Specify name of subdirectory for meta-information files</A>
