</MENU>
<LI><A NAME=ToC_333 HREF="#HDRAPISETS" >ICAPI application processing - Specify ICAPI applications to call during request processing</A>
<MENU>
<LI><A NAME=ToC_334 HREF="#HDRSERVERI" >ServerInit - Customize the Server Initialization step</A>
<LI><A NAME=ToC_337 HREF="#HDRPREEXIT" >PreExit - Customize the User Pre-exit step</A>
