<H1><A NAME="Header_543" HREF="icswgmst.html#ToC_543">Security</A></H1>
<HR>
<H1><A NAME="HDRSEC" HREF="icswgmst.html#ToC_544">Making your communications secure</A></H1>
<P>
If you have a secure server, you can use the
security built into it to
provide a secure environment for you and your users to
conduct business transactions.
<P>
This chapter provides an overview of security and explains
the different security protocols.
<P>
<P>Partial Table-of-Contents
